The ratio of Vimal's age and Arun's age is 3 : 5 and sum of their ages is 80 years. The ratio of their ages after 10 years will be: </br>विमल और अरुण की आयु का अनुपात 3:5 है और उनकी आयु का योगफल 80 वर्ष है. 10 साल बाद उनके आयु का अनुपात क्या होगा?
@2:3@1:2@3:2@3:5@@ Let Vimal's age and Arun's age be 3x years & 5x years respectively. </br> ATQ, </br> 3x + 5x = 80 </br> 8x = 80 </br> x = 10 </br> Vimal's age = 3x = 3 × 10 = 30 years </br> Arun's age = 5x = 5 × 10 = 50 years </br> After 10 years </br> Vimal's age = 30 + 10 = 40 years </br> Arun's age = 50 + 10 = 60 years </br> Ratio of their ages after 10 years 40 : 60 = 2 : 3.